snippet.title: Snow Horse - Steam and Xbox One Announcement Trailer!
snippet.description:
Welcome to Snow Horse, the snowboarding game you never asked for, where the points are made up and you are a horse riding a snowboard.

Coming Spring 2016

http://www.facebook.com/SnowHorseGame
http://www.twitter.com/kinifi
Song from the Trailer: https://soundcloud.com/jacobpernell/snow-horse

Plays Best on Alienware
